data.description: This beautiful North Phoenix home is perfectly set in a quiet and well-kept neighborhood. This 3 bed/2 bath home features a kitchen that is open to the family room, a living room, a 2-car garage, stunning grass yard with covered patio, RV gate and covered RV parking along the north side of the house. The back patio is wired for cable TV. Make this great home your own!
